metadata.name: レジ 𝑪𝒂𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒆𝒓
metadata.description:
𝐂𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐞𝐫 (𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐤 𝐓𝐢𝐦𝐞).
 
Everyday I go to work and do my best to speak to people clearly and with intention. Being a cashier is hard work so communication will be my strongest asset. It will make me stand out from others if i become a good communicator.
 
𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐤𝐭𝐢𝐦𝐞 𝐂𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧
 
Work time collection is a daily routine when somebody works. The only way to do great work is to love what you do.
